---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Physician Referral Program & Clinical Partnerships | Releaf MD" 
  description="Partner with Releaf MD for secure, ethical medical marijuana evaluations in the Tampa Bay area. We coordinate care with referring practices."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        🤝 Clinical Partnerships
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark leading-tight uppercase">Physician Referral Program</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Building trusted medical partnerships to provide compliant, compassionate, and evidence-based medical cannabis evaluations in the Tampa Bay community.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-whisper space-y-12">
        
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">A Trusted Extension of Your Care</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            At Releaf MD, we operate as a professional medical provider resource for your practice. Many chronic and debilitating conditions benefit from medical cannabis as an adjunctive therapy. We collaborate closely with primary care providers, oncologists, neurologists, psychiatrists, and pain specialists across the Tampa Bay area to ensure patients receive safe, compliant evaluations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Dr. King's Personal Statement & Community Roots -->
        <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-brand-primary/10">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-center md:items-start">
            <!-- Profile Photo -->
            <div class="w-full max-w-[180px] aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-whisper border border-brand-primary/10 flex-shrink-0">
              <img src="/dr-kelly-king.jpg" alt="Dr. Kelly Ennix King, MD" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4 text-center md:text-left">
              <div>
                <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-accent block mb-1">A Message from Our Medical Director</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Dr. Kelly Ennix King, MD</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs leading-relaxed italic">
                "As a medical doctor and U.S. Air Force veteran, clinical rigor, ethical standards, and community service are at the core of my practice. I established Releaf MD to provide patients in our local Tampa Bay community with a professional, compassionate clinic that stands apart. We treat medical cannabis evaluations with the same seriousness as any other medical specialty consultation."
              </p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                Releaf MD is actively involved in local community health outreach, supporting military veterans, and advocating for patient safety through educational workshops. We are proud partners in the Tampa Bay community health network.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Trust Pillars Grid -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase text-center">Why Physicians Trust Releaf MD</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover-lift flex flex-col justify-between">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-base mb-2">1. Strict Ethical Boundaries</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                  We do not sell medical cannabis, operate a dispensary, or maintain financial affiliations with any marijuana treatment center. Our focus remains 100% clinical.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover-lift flex flex-col justify-between">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-base mb-2">2. Coordination of Care Loop</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                  We maintain a continuous clinical loop. Upon request, Releaf MD sends detailed consultation summaries and treatment plans back to your office to keep patient records unified.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover-lift flex flex-col justify-between">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-base mb-2">3. Evidence-Based Dosing</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                  Dr. King provides patients with clear dosing instructions, emphasizes safety, and reviews potential pharmaceutical drug interactions to ensure patient wellness.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover-lift flex flex-col justify-between">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-base mb-2">4. Full Regulatory Compliance</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                  All evaluations strictly follow Florida Statute 381.986. We verify diagnosis codes, perform in-person visits, and complete registry entries with absolute compliance.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Referral Process Section -->
        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-10 space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">How to Refer a Patient</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            To prioritize patient privacy and maintain HIPAA compliance, we do not collect clinical or referral data online. You can refer patients directly through standard secure channels:
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-brand-mint/30 p-5 rounded-xl border border-brand-primary/10 text-center space-y-2">
              <span class="text-lg">📞</span>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-xs text-brand-dark uppercase">Call Our Office</h4>
              <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">
                Contact our intake coordinator directly to refer a patient.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-brand-primary">813-651-3492</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-brand-mint/30 p-5 rounded-xl border border-brand-primary/10 text-center space-y-2">
              <span class="text-lg">📠</span>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-xs text-brand-dark uppercase">Secure Fax</h4>
              <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">
                Fax clinical documentation or referral forms securely.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-brand-primary">833-375-3111</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-brand-mint/30 p-5 rounded-xl border border-brand-primary/10 text-center space-y-2">
              <span class="text-lg">✉️</span>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-xs text-brand-dark uppercase">Secure Email</h4>
              <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">
                Send encrypted medical records to our inbox.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-brand-primary">Medicalrecords@releafmd.com</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Direct CTA -->
        <div class="bg-brand-dark text-white p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-brand-accent space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-serif-headline text-brand-mint uppercase">Consult Directly with Dr. King</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            If you have complex patients or would like to discuss clinical protocols, Dr. Kelly Ennix King is happy to consult directly with referring physicians. Please call our main office line to coordinate a doctor-to-doctor call.
          </p>
          <div class="pt-2">
            <a href="tel:813-651-3492" class="inline-block bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-primary text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-xs uppercase transition-colors shadow-md active-press">
              Call Direct: 813-651-3492
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
